-- Delete Button --
Allows the played to delete the last letter he pressed
in case he pressed a doubled letter the delete button will delete all the letters added from that button

-- Scroll Bar --
After the player found a lot of words, instead for the window grow larger, we added a scrollbar and the player can scroll

-- 30 seconds warning --
When the player have 30 seconds left, a message will appear and warn him, while the message still opens
the letters will be hidden, so the player can't look for words when the clock isn't ticking